summary:
--- An Alcoholic\'s Dream! --- 
\"Modder\'s Resource Too!\"
Adds 30+ New Alcoholic Beverages In game and a Brewing Pot & Brewery with the ability to craft alcohol. Found at all cities and towns, Along with a \"SkyRum Salesman\" (A Fictional Liquor Company residing in Skyrim.)
descriptionHtml:
[center][img]https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/-dNQyJiRebq8/UNuckLBw8WI/AAAAAAAAAlY/bLiDfLNBR_c/s350/skyrum.png[/img][/center]

[i][b][center]***If you wish to use assets from this file in your own mod, feel free to use it as long as I get credit for it\'s creation. You must notify me of the mods development.***[/center][/b][/i]

[heading]Description:[/heading]

Adds 30+ New Alcoholic Beverages In game and a Brewery with the ability to craft alcohol. Found at the Four Shields Tavern in Dragon Bridge, along with new salesmen in all cities, large and small.

[heading]Known Bugs:[/heading]
In V3, the newest version, all land around the Whiterun Shipping Area, is black sand textured, completely on accident, It will not let me change it, If someone knows how to fix this, please let me know.

[heading]Update Content:[/heading]

[heading]Version 2.0 (V2.0):[/heading]
- Now includes custom new textures
- Now includes shipping docks

[heading]Version 3.0 (V3.0):[/heading]
- Now includes 30+ new Drinks, Stationary Textures (Barrels, Rugs, Banners, ETC)
- Backstory
- New stations in every city (Major & Minor)
- MONTHS of work put into this.

[heading]Version 3.5 (V3.5): TES5Edit Cleaned[/heading]
- TES5Edit Bug Cleaned
